description: The manager employs a “passive management” — or indexing — investment approach designed to track the performance of the underlying index, which was developed by Solactive A.G. (“Solactive” or the “index provider”) and Equileap. The underlying index is designed to track the U.S. large-, mid- and small-capitalization companies that have the highest Equileap Score. The fund is non-diversified.
name: IQ Engender Equality ETF
